snippet.title: Hana Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Available now for Playdate on itch and Playdate Store!

You are Jack, Captain of a ship that can traverse the Void which lies between universes.

You have traveled through Spacetime, searching for clues to help save the world from which you came.

Your next destination is Earth. Population 0.

Where did everyone go? Can finding out help save your home?

Explore a post-apocalyptic Earth in a glorious 1-bit adventure game for the Playdate handheld entertainment system.
